          "kind": "dialog",
          "lines": [
            "CONCORD REP: Welcome! No",
            "pressure at all. I used to",
            "train the old way too — years",
            "of waiting, hoping.",
            "CONCORD REP: We just think",
            "people deserve to skip the",
            "heartbreak. Strength, today.",
            "Have a wonderful afternoon."
          ]
        }
      ]
